model.publication
Class JournalPaper

java.lang.Object
  model.publication.Publication
      model.publication.JournalPaper
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class JournalPaper
extends Publication

The JournalPaper class represents journal paper entities and is subclass of Publication.

Besides attributes provided by Publication, journalName, issureNumber and pageNumber are provided by JournalPaper class.

                    java.lang.String uploaderUserName)
Initialises a newly created JournalPaper object with attributes of the passed parameters.

Parameters:
IDNumber - ID number of a JournalPaper, which is the primary key of a JournalPaper, and is in format of "JP0000".
publicationTitle - Title of this JournalPaper.
authorSet - A Set of author's full names, which may not be recorded in this system.
publishDate - The date this JournalPaper is published, namely, is uploaded to this system. And is in Date type.
journalName - The name of journal where this JournalPaper is published.
issueNumber - The issureNumber of the JournalPaper.
pageNumber - The pages that this JournalPaper is on the journal.
uploaderUserName - The userName of the one who uploads this JournalPaper.
